      <h2>A bond worth wearing</h2>
      <p>LilyTily started with a simple belief: the connection between a mother and her child shouldn't just live in photographs and memory — it deserves something you can wear, every single day.</p>
      <p>Every set is designed to feel classic rather than trendy: pieces a mother would choose for herself, sized down for her little one. No cartoon charms, no plastic. Just clean, well-made jewelry meant to be worn together, and held onto long after it's outgrown.</p>
